ity & Wild Shape","Description":"The Kholirahi Captain can use this feature Twice between rests. The Captain Can Transform into a beast of CR 1 or less for 7 hours, They revert if they fall unconcious or reach 0 hp. The Captain retains his intelligence, Charisma, and wisdom and other abilities but loses the ability to cast spells, though he may continue to Concentrate on a spell he has already cast. The captain may only speak or use his hands if his beast form allows him to do so. The rest of his stats and abilities are replaced with the beast's. His equipment merges with his new form\n\nAlternately the captain can use this feature to gain 45 temporary hit points, doubles the damage of his Memory of roots feature, his melee attacks deal 1d6 poison damage to any target they hit. These benefits last or ten minutes","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"The God King's Command","Description":"Any humanoid slain by the captain's Memory of Roots feature rises as a zombie with 1 hit point at the end of his turn and takes his turn immediately after the captain. It can only attack and remains animate for 1 hour, after which it collapses and dies","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"The God King's Protection","Description":"Critical hits don't do extra damage against the Captain","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Actions":[{"Title":"Shillelagh","Description":null,"isDamage":true,"isSpell":false,"attack":{"_Attack":"Melee Spell Attack","Bonus":"10","Reach":5,"RangeClose":0,"RangeFar":0,"Target":"one creature","HitDiceNumber":3,"HitDiceSize":8,"HitDamageBonus":5,"HitAverageDamage":18,"HitText":"","HitDamageType":"Bludgeoning"},"saveDC":0}],"_Reactions":[],"_Legendaries":[],"_advancedSpells":[],"_advancedSpellData":[],"Title":"","STR":8,"DEX":16,"CON":14,"INT":14,"WIS":20,"CHA":10,"proficency":5,"Speed":"30 ft.","AC":"17 (Kholirahi root magic)","HP":"104 (16d8 + 32)","CR":{"Index":18,"CR"